cboSuchOrt
Controls.RowSource: SELECT "_ALLE" AS kun_Ort, "Alle" AS kun_plz FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm WHERE kun_ID = 11100 UNION SELECT * From qryHlp_KunOrt ORDER BY kun_ort;

Controls.Name: kun_LKZ
Controls.RowSource: SELECT [_tblLKZ].ISO_2 AS LKZ, [_tblLKZ].Landesname_deu AS Staat, [_tblLKZ].Euro, [_tblLKZ].TelVorwahl AS Landesvorwahl, "Postfach" AS Postfachtxt FROM _tblLKZ;

Controls.Name: lst_KD
Controls.RowSource: SELECT tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Id, tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_Firma, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Nachname, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Vorname, tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_Handy FROM tbl_KD_Kundenstamm LEFT JOIN tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner ON tbl_KD_Kundenstamm.kun_IDF_PersonID = tbl_KD_Ansprechpartner.adr_ID WHERE kun_IstAktiv = TRUE ORDER BY kun_firma;
